Properties.Caption: Просмотр итогов по лицевым счетам
Properties.Tag: Select [K_UL_K_UL].[CUL_PARENT] As [Распорядитель], Max([K_UL_PARENT].[NUL]) As [Наименование распорядителя], [K_UL_K_UL].[CUL] As [Организация], Max([K_UL].[NUL]) As [Наименование организации], [K_LS].[CLS] As [Лицевой счет], [EX_K_LS].[DBN] As [Дата проводки], [K_ITEM].[CITEM] As [Тип обеспечения], Max([K_ITEM].[NITEM]) As [Наименование типа обеспечения], [K_CSUB].[CCSUB] As [Код субсидии], Max([K_CSUB].[NCSUB]) As [Наименование субсидии], [K_PKZ].[CPKZ] As [Код запроса], Max([K_PKZ].[NPKZ]) As [Наименование КЗ], [K_LSR].[NLSR] As [Коды БК], [EX_K_LS].[K_LSRID] As [Счет расходов], Max([EX_K_LS].[SUMM_CT_Y]) As [Поступления за год], Max([EX_K_LS].[SUMM_DT_Y]) As [Выбытия за год] From (((((((((([EX_K_LS] With (NoLock) Inner Join [Apps_Groups_K_UL_K_UL] With (NoLock) On ([EX_K_LS].[K_UL_K_ULID]=[Apps_Groups_K_UL_K_UL].[K_UL_K_ULID])) Inner Join [K_UL_K_UL] With (NoLock) On ([EX_K_LS].[K_UL_K_ULID]=[K_UL_K_UL].[K_UL_K_ULID])) Inner Join [K_UL] As [K_UL_PARENT] With (NoLock) On ([K_UL_K_UL].[K_ULID_PARENT]=[K_UL_PARENT].[K_ULID])) Inner Join [K_UL] With (NoLock) On ([K_UL_K_UL].[K_ULID]=[K_UL].[K_ULID])) Inner Join [K_LS] With (NoLock) On ([EX_K_LS].[K_LSID]=[K_LS].[K_LSID])) Inner Join [K_ITEM] With (NoLock) On ([EX_K_LS].[K_ITEMID_TO]=[K_ITEM].[K_ITEMID])) Inner Join [K_PS] With (NoLock) On ([EX_K_LS].[K_PSID]=[K_PS].[K_PSID])) Left Join [K_LSR] With (NoLock) On ([EX_K_LS].[K_LSRID]=[K_LSR].[K_LSRID])) Left Join [K_CSUB] With (NoLock) On ([EX_K_LS].[K_CSUBID]=[K_CSUB].[K_CSUBID])) Left Join [K_PKZ] With (NoLock) On ([EX_K_LS].[K_PKZID]=[K_PKZ].[K_PKZID])) Where [Apps_Groups_K_UL_K_UL].[Apps_GroupsID]=GetApps_GroupsID() And |0 Group by [K_UL_K_UL].[CUL_PARENT], [K_UL_K_UL].[CUL], [K_LS].[CLS], [EX_K_LS].[DBN], [K_ITEM].[CITEM], [K_CSUB].[CCSUB], [K_PKZ].[CPKZ], [K_LSR].[NLSR], [EX_K_LS].[K_LSRID] Order by |1
Properties.Name: Просмотр итогов по лицевым счетам
